WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.070
Incredible. Do you think anybody's up? I know it's late or early wherever you

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:05.830
are, but some parts of the world are

00:00:05.840 --> 00:00:07.510
awake right now. So, I just thought I'd

00:00:07.520 --> 00:00:09.990
pray with y'all a little bit. What I

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.510
felt in my spirit

00:00:13.520 --> 00:00:15.270
as we're waiting for some other people

00:00:15.280 --> 00:00:17.110
to show up with us.

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:18.590
I don't know how many people would be up

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:20.750
right now, but

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:23.310
this is the urgency that I felt

00:00:23.320 --> 00:00:25.230
yesterday.

00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:26.910
I was in such deep prayer and

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:30.150
intercession concerning this war that

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:31.830
we're about to see.

00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:35.830
This is a lot more serious than what

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:38.390
people realize.

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:43.070
And so

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:45.990
as we pray now, we pray for the safety

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.910
of our troops. We pray for the safety of

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:52.470
any kind of ground invasion.

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.390
I really truly believe we're about to

00:00:57.400 --> 00:00:59.350
see a great escalation of things.

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:01.910
Remember I told you when the tariffs and

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:04.910
all the things with the Supreme Court

00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:06.950
fell

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:09.390
and I said when that happened, I said

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:11.590
it's time for plan B. Do you remember

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:12.910
that?

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:15.470
I told you specifically what I saw when

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:18.070
the Supreme Court failed.

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:21.750
I said, What's plan B?

00:01:21.760 --> 00:01:24.910
And plan B was this and exactly what I

00:01:24.920 --> 00:01:27.630
told you all in the spirit and

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:29.470
what I've been praying over privately in

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:30.510
the days

00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:32.190
past. I heard

00:01:32.190 --> 00:01:32.200
the Lord

00:01:32.200 --> 00:01:35.230
say you must pray over

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:38.070
the Supreme Court decision for this

00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:39.990
will be another domino. This is what's

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:42.510
coming next, war,

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:46.470
and I saw

00:01:46.480 --> 00:01:48.510
this all unfolding like we're

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:50.190
seeing right now

00:01:50.200 --> 00:01:52.390
and I saw Israel strike first.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.270
I

00:01:54.280 --> 00:01:55.910
saw

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:57.990
President Trump wanted to go about it

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.430
diplomatically

00:01:59.440 --> 00:02:01.710
and Benjamin wanted to push

00:02:01.720 --> 00:02:03.510
the button. I saw him push the button

00:02:03.520 --> 00:02:07.590
and then I saw anti-semitism

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:11.310
come to an all-time high for Israel in

00:02:11.320 --> 00:02:13.710
the days ahead if anybody remembers and

00:02:13.720 --> 00:02:16.710
I said this will be by God's hand and there

00:02:16.710 --> 00:02:16.720
will

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.910
be so many people leave New

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:22.910
York and other places in the days ahead

00:02:22.920 --> 00:02:25.950
to come back to the motherland

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.230
Israel,

00:02:27.240 --> 00:02:30.270
Jerusalem and I saw people leaving

00:02:30.280 --> 00:02:33.030
from all over and they needed finances

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:34.790
and there were ministries that

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:36.950
needed finances to bring the people

00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:38.830
home

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:40.870
and I saw this coming

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:43.190
for great anti-semitism

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:44.110
and

00:02:44.110 --> 00:02:44.120
protests

00:02:44.120 --> 00:02:46.430
and riots will come in the days

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:48.910
ahead. And then the Lord showed me going

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:53.470
up clear into the 250th anniversary,

00:02:53.480 --> 00:02:55.670
praying over our nation, what was one of

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:59.030
the major things I said to pray over

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:01.150
Easter

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:04.270
after Ramadan,

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:06.990
praying for a Ramadan because after Ramadan and

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.470
the things that I saw leading up to this

00:03:09.480 --> 00:03:11.390
for

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:14.710
attacks against our own homeland soil

00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:17.070
and I even brought this up not even

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:18.950
3 or 4 hours ago in the

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:21.790
live of what I saw. I've

00:03:21.790 --> 00:03:21.800
had

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:25.350
to be very

00:03:25.350 --> 00:03:25.360
careful

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:28.310
because of the sensitivity of the things

00:03:28.320 --> 00:03:30.590
I have been seeing because I don't want

00:03:30.600 --> 00:03:33.550
to put our troops in harm's way. I have

00:03:33.560 --> 00:03:34.910
not

00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:37.030
let these things out

00:03:37.040 --> 00:03:40.550
because of the sensitivity of it and how

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:43.350
I believe how accurate it truly is

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:45.590
concerning certain things.

00:03:46.880 --> 00:03:48.950
And so we see it now.

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:50.910
I believe

00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:53.470
in the name of Jesus, we pray over our

00:03:53.480 --> 00:03:56.790
military bases. We pray over our

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:59.870
battleships. We pray over any kind

00:03:59.880 --> 00:04:02.750
of retaliation. You know what would be

00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:05.830
amazing? What would be just God is if

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:08.270
they all just laid down their arms

00:04:08.280 --> 00:04:10.310
because they want to be free from the

00:04:10.320 --> 00:04:11.950
ayatollah Khomeini.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:14.190
Wouldn't that be awesome if they just

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:16.110
say, You know what? We're not going to

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:18.150
fight back. We don't want to retaliate.

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:20.590
We want a new government. We want a new

00:04:20.600 --> 00:04:23.670
leader. And so we lay down our arms.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.590
We're not fighting back the Americans.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:28.790
We're excited just to get rid of this

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:31.070
dictator.

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:33.750
Wouldn't that be God?

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.590
I've seen bigger things. I've

00:04:36.590 --> 00:04:36.600
been

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:37.870
saying that that

00:04:37.870 --> 00:04:37.880
could

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:40.750
happen. That's a huge thing.

00:04:40.760 --> 00:04:43.790
But I just believe that it could happen.

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:45.430
You know what? President Trump, they're

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:47.870
wanting to liberate us. Let's just

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:49.910
don't fight back. Let's

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:52.310
get because even whatever he said, I want to

00:04:52.320 --> 00:04:54.870
play this what he just said. He just had

00:04:54.880 --> 00:04:56.950
a press briefing. Did anybody watch

00:04:56.960 --> 00:04:59.990
that? What he just said at

00:04:59.990 --> 00:05:00.000
Mar-a-Lago

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.350
in Florida.

00:05:08.680 --> 00:05:11.550
Play what he said. He

00:05:11.560 --> 00:05:22.310
just basically declared war.

00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:24.350
A short time ago,

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:27.190
the United States military began

00:05:27.200 --> 00:05:31.870
major combat operations in Iran.

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:34.510
Our objective is to defend the American

00:05:34.520 --> 00:05:37.470
people by eliminating imminent threats

00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:42.190
from the Iranian regime, a vicious group

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:44.430
of very hard,

00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:46.550
terrible people.

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.510
Its menacing activities directly

00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:50.990
endanger the United States, our troops,

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.870
our bases overseas, and our allies

00:05:53.880 --> 00:05:55.510
throughout the world.

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:58.310
For 47 years, the Iranian regime has

00:05:58.320 --> 00:06:01.350
chanted death to America and

00:06:01.350 --> 00:06:01.360
waged

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:04.310
an unending campaign of bloodshed and

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:05.830
mass murder,

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:08.270
targeting the United States, our troops,

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:10.430
and the innocent people in many, many

00:06:10.440 --> 00:06:11.990
countries.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.470
Among the regime's very first acts was

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:17.190
to back a violent takeover of the US

00:06:17.200 --> 00:06:19.070
embassy in Tehran,

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:21.870
holding dozens of American hostages for

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:24.830
444 days.

00:06:24.840 --> 00:06:28.710
In 1983, Iran's proxies carried out the

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:30.910
Marine barracks bombing in Beirut that

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:35.310
killed 241 American military personnel.

00:06:35.320 --> 00:06:37.990
In 2000, they knew and were probably

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.950
involved with the attack on the USS

00:06:40.960 --> 00:06:43.870
Cole. Many died.

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:46.110
Iranian forces killed and maimed

00:06:46.120 --> 00:06:48.270
hundreds of American service members in

00:06:48.280 --> 00:06:50.550
Iraq. The regime's proxies have

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:52.750
continued to launch countless attacks

00:06:52.760 --> 00:06:55.590
against American forces stationed in the

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:58.350
Middle East in recent years, as well as

00:06:58.360 --> 00:07:00.830
US naval and commercial vessels in

00:07:00.840 --> 00:07:03.390
international shipping lanes.

00:07:03.400 --> 00:07:06.590
It's been mass terror and we're not

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:09.150
going to put up with it any longer.

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:12.910
From Lebanon to Yemen and Syria to Iraq,

00:07:12.920 --> 00:07:15.230
the regime has armed, trained, and

00:07:15.240 --> 00:07:18.030
funded terrorist militias that have

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:22.110
soaked the earth with blood and guts.

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:25.150
And it was Iran's proxy Hamas that

00:07:25.160 --> 00:07:27.790
launched the monstrous October 7th

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:30.070
attacks on Israel,

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.550
slaughtering more than 1,000 innocent

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:34.910
people, including 46 Americans, while

00:07:34.920 --> 00:07:38.430
taking 12 of our citizens hostage. It

00:07:38.440 --> 00:07:41.910
was brutal, something like the world has

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:44.070
never seen before.

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:46.390
Iran is the world's number one state

00:07:46.400 --> 00:07:49.310
sponsor of terror and just recently

00:07:49.320 --> 00:07:51.590
killed tens of thousands of its own

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:53.390
citizens on the street as they

00:07:53.400 --> 00:07:55.870
protested. It has always been the policy

00:07:55.880 --> 00:07:59.190
of the United States in particular my

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:00.710
administration

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.830
that this terrorist regime can never

00:08:02.840 --> 00:08:05.110
have a nuclear weapon.

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:08.430
I'll say it again. They can never have a

00:08:08.440 --> 00:08:10.790
nuclear weapon.

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:13.790
That is why in operation midnight hammer

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:16.990
last June we obliterated the regime's

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:19.710
nuclear program at

00:08:19.710 --> 00:08:19.720
Fordo,

00:08:19.720 --> 00:08:22.790
Natanz and Isfahan.

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:25.470
After that attack we warned them never

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:27.870
to resume their malicious pursuit of

00:08:27.880 --> 00:08:29.510
nuclear weapons

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:33.630
and we sought repeatedly to make a deal.

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:36.469
We tried. They wanted to do it. They

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:38.750
didn't want to do it again. They wanted

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:40.510
to do it. They didn't want to do it.

00:08:40.520 --> 00:08:42.230
They didn't know what was happening.

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:45.310
They just wanted to practice evil.

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:48.430
But Iran refused, just as it has for

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:50.870
decades and decades.

00:08:50.870 --> 00:08:50.880
They've

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:53.070
rejected every opportunity to

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:56.230
renounce their nuclear ambitions,

00:08:56.240 --> 00:08:58.630
and we can't take it anymore.

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:01.430
Instead, they attempted to rebuild their

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:04.190
nuclear program and to continue

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:07.350
developing long range missiles that can

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:09.230
now threaten our

00:09:09.240 --> 00:09:11.670
very good friends and allies in Europe,

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:14.790
our troops stationed overseas and could

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:18.270
soon reach the American homeland.

00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:21.110
Just imagine how emboldened this regime

00:09:21.120 --> 00:09:24.070
would be if they ever had and actually

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:26.710
were armed with nuclear weapons as a

00:09:26.720 --> 00:09:29.950
means to deliver their message.

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:32.030
For these reasons, the United States

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:34.510
military has undertaken a massive and

00:09:34.520 --> 00:09:37.710
ongoing operation to prevent this very

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:40.630
wicked, radical dictatorship from

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:42.750
threatening America and our core

00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:45.870
national security interests. We are

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:48.270
going to destroy their missiles and raze

00:09:48.280 --> 00:09:51.270
their missile industry to the ground. It

00:09:51.280 --> 00:09:55.750
will be totally again obliterated. We

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:57.910
are going to annihilate their navy. We

00:09:57.910 --> 00:09:57.920
are

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.510
going to ensure that the region's

00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:02.910
terrorist proxies can no longer

00:10:02.920 --> 00:10:05.670
destabilize the region or the world and

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:07.990
attack our forces and no longer use

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:12.110
their IEDs or roadside bombs as they

00:10:12.120 --> 00:10:15.070
are sometimes called to so gravely

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:17.630
wound and kill thousands and thousands

00:10:17.640 --> 00:10:21.110
of people including many Americans. And

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:24.430
we will ensure that Iran does not obtain

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:27.710
a nuclear weapon. It's a very simple

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:30.990
message. They will never have a nuclear

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:32.390
weapon.

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:34.950
This regime will soon learn that no one

00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:37.070
should challenge the strength and might

00:10:37.080 --> 00:10:40.350
of the United States armed forces.

00:10:40.360 --> 00:10:42.830
I built and rebuilt our military in my

00:10:42.840 --> 00:10:45.310
first administration,

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:47.630
and there is no military on earth even

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:49.630
close to its power,

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:52.070
strength, or sophistication.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:53.990
My administration has taken every

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:57.510
possible step to minimize the risk to US

00:10:57.520 --> 00:10:59.470
personnel in the region.

00:10:59.480 --> 00:11:01.870
Even so, and I do not make this

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:03.550
statement lightly,

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:07.230
the Iranian regime seeks to kill.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:09.510
The lives of courageous American heroes

00:11:09.520 --> 00:11:13.150
may be lost and we may have casualties.

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:15.590
That often happens in war. But we're

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:18.150
doing this not for now. We're doing this

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:20.910
for the future. And it is a noble

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:22.230
mission.

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:24.590
We pray for every service member as they

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:27.070
selflessly risk their lives to ensure

00:11:27.080 --> 00:11:29.710
that Americans and our children will

00:11:29.720 --> 00:11:32.030
never be threatened by a nuclear

00:11:32.030 --> 00:11:32.040
armed

00:11:32.040 --> 00:11:33.270
Iran.

00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:35.790
We ask God to protect all of our heroes

00:11:35.800 --> 00:11:37.350
in harm's way.

00:11:37.360 --> 00:11:40.030
And we trust that with his help, the

00:11:40.040 --> 00:11:43.070
men and women of the armed forces will

00:11:43.080 --> 00:11:44.350
prevail.

00:11:44.360 --> 00:11:46.270
We have the greatest in the world and

00:11:46.280 --> 00:11:48.590
they will prevail. To the members of the

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:51.750
Islamic Revolutionary Guard, the armed

00:11:51.760 --> 00:11:54.790
forces, and all of the police, I say

00:11:54.800 --> 00:11:57.390
tonight that you must lay down your

00:11:57.400 --> 00:12:00.550
weapons and have complete immunity, or

00:12:00.560 --> 00:12:04.110
in the alternative, face certain death.

00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:07.150
So, lay down your arms, you will be

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:11.030
treated fairly with total immunity, or

00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:13.870
you will face certain death.

00:12:13.880 --> 00:12:15.910
Finally, to the great proud people of

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:18.790
Iran, I say tonight that the hour of

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:20.950
your freedom is at hand.

00:12:20.960 --> 00:12:23.310
Stay sheltered. Don't leave your home.

00:12:23.320 --> 00:12:25.710
It's very dangerous outside. Bombs will

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:28.070
be dropping everywhere. When we are

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:30.190
finished, take over your government. It

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:33.350
will be yours to take. This will be

00:12:33.360 --> 00:12:36.110
probably your only chance for

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:37.829
generations.

00:12:37.839 --> 00:12:39.270
For many years, you have asked for

00:12:39.280 --> 00:12:42.470
America's help, but you never got it. No

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:44.790
president was willing to do what I am

00:12:44.800 --> 00:12:47.390
willing to do tonight. Now you have a

00:12:47.400 --> 00:12:49.350
president who is giving you what you

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:52.910
want. So let's see how you respond.

00:12:52.920 --> 00:12:56.070
America is backing you with overwhelming

00:12:56.070 --> 00:12:56.080
strength

00:12:56.080 --> 00:12:58.870
and devastating force. Now is the time

00:12:58.880 --> 00:13:01.150
to seize control of your destiny and to

00:13:01.160 --> 00:13:03.910
unleash the prosperous and glorious

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:07.350
future that is close within your reach.

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:09.990
This is the moment for action. Do not

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:13.150
let it pass. May God bless the brave men

00:13:13.160 --> 00:13:15.990
and women of America's armed forces. May

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:19.310
God bless the United States of America.

00:13:19.320 --> 00:13:23.230
May God bless you all. Thank you.

